[{"date":"1953-11-21","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c1/e6/634638_j3yTt.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c1/e6/634638_j3yTt.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c1/e6/634638_j3yTt.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c1/e6/634638_j3yTt.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c1/e6/634638_j3yTt.jpg"},"summary":"　　某天，邮递员送来信件和包裹。兴奋的汤姆冲出房门，却发现这些都是杰瑞的东西。趁着小老鼠不在，汤姆偷偷拆开包裹，发现里面是一本书，上面写着“与汤姆一起生活（Life with Tom）”。原来这是杰瑞写的传记，而根据收音机中的介绍，似乎里面记录了不少汤姆与杰瑞搞笑有趣的事情。汤姆好奇的翻开书，里面讲述了《Cat Fishin’》中小老鼠被当作鱼饵扔进池塘，继而引发一场乱斗的故事；还有《The Little Orphan’》杰瑞带着孤儿尼波斯爬上餐桌觅食被汤姆围捕的经历；以及《Kitty Foiled》中汤姆驾驶火车要从杰瑞身上碾过反遭厄运的糗事。\r\n　　看到记载了自己那么多的倒霉事，汤姆非常生气……","name":"Life with Tom","name_cn":"小说风波","tags":[{"name":"1950s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"小说风波"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1953年11月21日"},{"key":"片长","value":"8分钟"},{"key":"IMDb","value":"tt0045999"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":2,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.5},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":0,"dropped":0,"wish":0,"collect":5,"doing":0},"id":634638,"eps":0,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1953-11-11","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/cb/83/383846_UaQLQ.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/cb/83/383846_UaQLQ.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/cb/83/383846_UaQLQ.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/cb/83/383846_UaQLQ.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/cb/83/383846_UaQLQ.jpg"},"summary":"Chip 'n Dale live next door to a zoo and spot the elephant's stash of peanuts. They go after them, but both the elephant and his keeper, Donald, are too clever. Then the boys realize the visitors throw peanuts, so 